in%20real%20time.%20The%20program%20also%20connects%20to%20other%20Google%20Workspace%20apps%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-convert-powerpoint-to-google-slides%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Slides%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google%20Docs%2C%20and%20Gmail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aecb8ed5-8fda-4bda-a006-8ed7d926774a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Google%20Sheets%20used%20for%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Sheets%20can%20be%20used%20for%20any%20purpose%20that%20typically%20involves%20a%20spreadsheet.%20This%20might%20include%20creating%20budgets%2C%20making%20calculations%2C%20performing%20analyses%2C%20drafting%20charts%2C%20or%20managing%20projects%20or%20tasks.%20It%20can%20be%20used%20for%20business%20or%20personal%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20most%20likely%20don't%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20whether%20Google%20Sheets%20has%20the%20bandwidth%20for%20your%20dataset.%20Google%20Sheets%20can%20handle%20up%20to%2010%20million%20cells%20or%2018%2C287%20columns%20%E2%80%94%20far%20more%20than%20most%20users%20will%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292cd9203-c7a6-42c6-ad7d-fd7686da7957%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20Google%20Sheets%20and%20Microsoft%20Excel%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Sheets%20is%20part%20of%20Google%20Workspace%2C%20while%20Microsoft%20Excel%20is%20part%20of%20Microsoft%20365.%20Both%20let%20you%20create%20spreadsheets%20for%20various%20purposes%2C%20such%20as%20bookkeeping%20or%20planning%2C%20and%20they%20share%20some%20similar%20features%2C%20such%20as%20writing%20equations%20and%20presenting%20data%20in%20an%20organized%2C%20easy-to-understand%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Sheets%20is%20free%20and%20easily%20allows%20multiple%20users%20to%20collaborate%20in%20a%20spreadsheet%20in%20real%20time%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20fairly%20simplistic.%20Microsoft%20Excel%20is%20a%20m