%2Ftopic%2Fhemant-soren%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20arrested%20in%20January%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20-%20has%20withdrawn%20an%20interim%20bail%20plea%20filed%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20questions%20over%20non-disclosure%20of%20facts%2C%20specifically%20that%20a%20Ranchi%20special%20court%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20complaint%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fkapil-sibal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKapil%20Sibal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Soren%2C%20withdrew%20the%20application%20after%20an%20irate%20court%20warned%20it%20would%20otherwise%20dismiss%20the%20plea.%20This%20means%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20leader%2C%20who%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2F2024-lok-sabha-election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%20Jharkhand's%2014%20seats%20was%20spread%20across%20four%20phases.%20Polling%20for%20seven%20has%20been%20completed%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20to%20vote%20across%20the%20sixth%20and%20seventh%20(final)%20phases%20-%20on%20May%2025%20and%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Supreme%20Court%20Said%20To%20Kapil%20Sibal%20Today%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20hearing%20the%20court%20-%20which%20asked%20several%20tough%20questions%20of%20Mr%20Sibal%20-%20also%20junked%20a%20petition%20challenging%20Hemant%20Soren's%20arrest%3B%20the%20JMM%20leader%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20which%20has%20alleged%20that%20he%2C%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20ran%20a%20scheme%20to%20manipulate%20records%2C%20v