0Of%20Facts%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20the%20Jharkhand%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20Mr%20Soren's%20plea%20challenging%20his%20arrest%3B%20it%20pointed%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Babundance%20of%20documents%20that%20lay%20foundation%20for%20the%20arrest%20and%20remand%20of%20petitioner%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20central%20agency%20and%20sought%20its%20response%20to%20an%20interim%20bail%20plea%20filed%20before%20it%20on%20grounds%20the%20High%20Court%20was%20delaying%20delivery%20of%20its%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20High%20Court%20finally%20delivered%20its%20judgement%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20closed%20the%20petition%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Datta%20noted%20it%20had%20now%20become%20%26quot%3Binfructuous%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-disposes-of-hemant-sorens-petition-seeking-interim-bail-5631340%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Disposes%20Of%20Hemant%20Soren's%20Petition%20Seeking%20Interim%20Bail%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20had%20then%20sought%20interim%20bail%20-%20while%20the%20High%20Court%20delivered%20its%20verdict%20-%20to%20campaign%20for%20his%20party%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Mr%20Sibal%20had%20then%20requested%20that%20the%20bail%20plea%20and%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20High%20Court%20verdict%20be%20heard%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-approaches-supreme-court-against-high-court-verdict-5599425%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren%20Approaches%20Supreme%20Court%20Against%20High%20Court%20Verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C