l%20Transport%20Office%20(RTO)%20for%20the%20registration%20process%20after%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20it%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20owner%20to%20get%20it%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoad%20tax%20is%20exempted%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20so%20the%20registration%20of%20this%20vehicle%20was%20on%20Rs%201%2C758%20-%20Rs%201%2C500%20hypothecation%20fees%2C%20Rs%20200%20smart%20card%20RC%20fees%20and%20Rs%2058%20postal%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20driving%20the%20car%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20realtor%2C%20who%20has%20been%20arrested.%20The%20teen%20had%20been%20released%20on%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20his%20arrest%2C%20with%20a%20300-word%20essay%20ordered%20as%20punishment%2C%20which%20triggered%20massive%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owners%20of%20two%20bars%20where%20the%20minor%20was%20served%20alcohol%20before%20he%20ran%20over%20two%20persons%20have%20also%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%20took%20place%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Sunday%20morning%20in%20Pune's%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Porsche%2C%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20at%20over%20200%20km%20per%20hour%20speed%2C%20hit%20the%20bike%20on%20which%20two%2024-year-old%20techies%20were%20returning%20home%20after%20a%20party.%20Ashwini%20was%20thrown%20about%2020%20feet%20in%20the%20air%20and%20landed%20hard%2C%20said%20an%20eyewitness.%20Aneesh%20was%20thrown%20at%20a%20parked%20car%20and%20suffered%20serious%20injuries.%20Both%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716364740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fo9pv5kdk_pune-porsche-accident_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-porsche-accident-porsche-registration-stalled-since-march-over-non-payment-of-rs-1-758-fee-5718515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%