0rained-off%20game%2C%20RCB%20have%20notched%20up%20six%20consecutive%20wins%20to%20sound%20a%20warning%20to%20their%20rivals%20that%20they%20mean%20business%20in%20the%20playoffs.%20But%2C%20could%20rain%20spoil%20RCB's%20stunning%20run%20in%20the%20league%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20reaching%20the%20Qualifier%202%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20if%20RCB%20vs%20RR%20Eliminator%20Gets%20Washed%20Out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rule%2013.7.3%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20Match%20Playing%20Conditions%2C%20an%20extra%20120%20minutes%20or%20two%20hours%20are%20available%20to%20finish%20a%20match%20because%20of%20rain%20delay.%20The%20rule%20was%20in%20place%20even%20for%20league-stage%20matches.%20But%2C%20in%20playoffs%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Day%20option%20is%20also%20available%2C%20meaning%20there%20will%20be%20an%20additional%20day%20in%20place%20for%20the%20Eliminator%20between%20RCB%20and%20RR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20play-off%20matches%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20extra%20time%20referred%20to%20above%2C%20there%20may%20be%20reserve%20days%20(on%20which%20an%20incomplete%20play-off%20match%20shall%20be%20completed).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20previous%20editions%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20there's%20a%20Reserve%20Day%20in%20place%20for%20all%20playoffs%20matches%20this%20season%2C%20including%20the%20final%20which%20will%20be%20held%20on%20May%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20on%20the%20reserve%20day%2C%20the%20match%20will%20be%20played%20from%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20if%20no%20play%20is%20possible%20even%20after%20the%20option%20of%20Reserve%20Day%20is%20explored%2C%20with%20the%20organisers%20failing%20to%20conduct%20even%20a%20Super%20Over%2C%20in%20such%20a%20case%20the%20team%20that%20finished%20higher%20in%20the%20league%20stage%20will%20go%20through.%20Hence%2C%20it's%20advantage%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20if%20the%20Eliminator%20gets%2