r%20dowry%20worth%2C%20the%20'calculator'%20shows%20the%20visitor%20stats%20about%20dowry%20deaths%20in%20India.%20Respect%20and%20wonderful%20idea%20%40AnupamMittal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EInitially%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20Dowry%20calculator%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEQr0sQBWQD%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEQr0sQBWQD%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20segment%20of%20the%20site%20show%20users%20how%20much%20they%20are%20worth%20in%20the%20'dowry'%20stakes.%20When%20you%20enter%20your%20details%20like%20educational%20qualification%20and%20income%2C%20you%20are%20in%20for%20a%20surprise.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnInstead%20of%20showing%20their%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fa9jw1P3oBf%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fa9jw1P3oBf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20The%20Cancer%20Doctor%20(%40DoctorHussain96)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDoctorHussain96%2Fstatus%2F1792257166683894236%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20users%20also%20liked%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShameful%20to%20see%20that%20people%20are%20still%20taking%20dowry%20in%20some%20form%20or%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BLogged%20in%20accounts%20using%20the%20calculator%20should%20be%20reported%20to%20authorities.%20All%20accounts%20should%20require%20a%20signed%20affidavit%20saying%20they%20won't%20accept%20dowry%20in%20any%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFantastic!%20No%20one%20should%20ideally%20click%20on%20the%20'Dowry%20calculator'%20in%20the%20portal.%20They%20should%20also%20show%20how%20many%20people%20have%20used%20the%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20third%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20users%20commented%3A%20%26quot%3BDeserves%20an%20award!%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDil%20jeet%20liya%20sahab%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matrimonial%20site%20launched%20the%20innovative%20campaign%20against%20dowry%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716362700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fu9pd1cq8_marriage-generic-istock_625x300_11_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fshaadi-coms-dowry-calculator-amuses-internet-know-what-its-all-about-5719049%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20dowry%20calculator%20actually%20delivers%20a%20powerful%20message%20that%20has%20left%20Internet%20amused.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fshaadi-coms-dowry-calculator-amuses-internet-know-what-its-all-about-5719049%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fshaadi-coms-dowry-calculator-amuses-internet-know-what-its-all-about-5719049%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fshaadi-coms-dowry-calculator-amuses-internet-know-what-its-all-about-5719049%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20class%20and%20experience%20like%20that%2C%20you%20can't%20replace%20Virat%3A%20Ponting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716362689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110326230%2Cimgsize-44330.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fwith-class-and-experience-like-that-you-cant-replace-virat-kohli-ricky-ponting%2Farticleshow%2F110326317.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ricky%20Ponting%20supports%20Virat%20Kohli%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20emphasizing%20his%20IPL%20success%2C%20value%20to%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20and%20reliability%20in%20crucial%20game%20moments.%20With%20708%20runs%20from%2014%20innings%2C%20Kohli%20le