the%20length%20is%20difficult%20to%20rectify%20and%2For%20monitor.%20The%20length%20of%20the%20skirt%20is%20not%20in%20line%20with%20the%20school%20uniform%20and%20we%20are%20at%20a%20point%20now%20where%20this%20must%20be%20addressed.%20As%20such%2C%20we%20are%20reviewing%20the%20wearing%20of%20skirts%20for%20September%202024%20and%20considering%20a%20move%20to%20trousers%20for%20all.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20went%20on%20to%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20a%20uniform%20worn%20without%20modification%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20ensure%20equality.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20pupils%20feeling%20vulnerable%20and%20stressed%20by%20the%20pressure%20they%20feel%20to%20wear%20the%20latest%20trend%20or%20status%20symbol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWearing%20a%20uniform%20as%20expected%2C%20dilutes%20the%20status%20placed%20on%20expensive%20shoes%2C%20labels%2C%20or%20length%20of%20skirt.%20We%20strive%20to%20shift%20the%20emphasis%20of%20competition%20and%20status%2C%20to%20create%20a%20feeling%20of%20collective%20pride%20and%20of%20support%20for%20peers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20said%20it%20will%20make%20its%20final%20decision%20after%20the%20May%20half-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20decision%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20several%20angry%20parents%20who%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20slam%20the%20move.%20Many%20said%20they%20''are%20'not%20happy'%20that%20the%20school%20wants%20to%20'dictate'%20what%20young%20pupils%20can%20wear.%20One%20woman%20said%2C%20''It%20seems%20ridiculous%20that%20girls%20have%20no%20dress%20or%20pinafore%20option%20and%20to%20be%20asked%20to%20dress%20in%20a%20uniform%20that%20will%20make%20some%20girls%20feel%20uncomfortable%2Fnot%20themselves.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BYoung%20girls%20especially%20in%20the%20junior%20school%20are%20suffering%20because%20teachers%20can't%20handle%20the%20discipline%20it%20takes%20to%20teach%20kids%20to%20ro