%3EEyewitnesses%20said%20how%20one%20victim%20was%20thrown%2020%20feet%20into%20the%C2%A0air%2C%C2%A0while%C2%A0the%20other%20was%20flung%C2%A0into%20a%20parked%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20reports%2C%20the%2017-year-old%20was%20behind%20the%20wheel%C2%A0at%20the%20time%20of%C2%A0the%20crash.%20Authorities%20claim%C2%A0he%C2%A0was%20drunk%20while%20driving.%20The%20Pune%20police%20arrested%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20bar%20for%20allowing%20underage%20drinking%20on%20their%20premises.%C2%A0Maharashtra's%C2%A0legal%20age%20for%20drinking%20is%2025%2C%20making%20the%20incident%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20are%20the%20drunk%20driving%20laws%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EAlcohol%20limit%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriving%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol%20or%20drugs%20is%20prohibited%C2%A0under%20Section%20185%20of%20the%20Motor%20Vehicle%20Act%201988.%20The%20legal%20alcohol%20limit%20in%20India%C2%A0is%20set%C2%A0at%200.03%25%20per%20100ml%20of%20blood.%20If%20more%20than%2030mg%20of%20alcohol%20or%20drugs%20in%20a%20sample%20of%20100%20ml%20blood%20is%20detected%2C%20it%20is%20considered%20illegal%20and%20a%20punishable%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EPenalty%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20caught%20driving%20while%20intoxicated%20or%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20drugs%2C%20the%20offender%20faces%20serious%20penalties.%C2%A0According%20to%20Section%20185%20of%20The%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%2C%201988%2C%C2%A0if%20it%20is%20your%20first%20time%20getting%20caught%20drinking%20and%20driving%20in%20India%2C%20you%20could%20be%20looking%20at%20six%20months%20of%20jail%20time%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20%E2%82%B910%2C000.%20Before%202019%2C%20the%20fine%20for%20a%20first%20offence%20was%20%E2%82%B92%2C000.%C2%A0For%20a%20second%20offence%2C%C2%A0you%20could%20spend%20up%20to%202%20years%20in%20jail%20and%C2%A0be%20fined%C2%A0%E2%82%B915%2C000%20(up%20from%20%E2%82%B93%2C000).%C2%A0Repeat%20offenders%20might%20also%20face%20penalties%20related%20to%20their%20driving%20licenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%202019%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%2C%20penalties%20apply%20to%20all%20vehicle%20types%2C%20including%20two-wheelers%2C%20three-wheelers%20and%20commercial%20ones.%20Insurance%20claims%20are%20not%20valid%20for%20accidents%20resulting%20from%20drunk%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3ELegal%20age%20for%20alcohol%20consumption%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20legal%20age%20for%20drinking%20ranges%20from%2018%20years%20to%2025%20years%2C%20varying%20across%20states.%20Goa%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20allow%20drinking%20from%C2%A0the%20age%20of%C2%A018%2C%20while%20states%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20set%20the%20limit%20at%2025%20years.%20States%20like%20Assam%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%C2%A0west%20Bengal%20have%20a%20legal%20drinking%20age%20of%2021%20years.%20Meanwhile%2C%20some%20states%2C%20like%20Gujarat%2C%20have%20imposed%20complete%20bans%20on%20alcohol.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716362040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3e1bkph8_car-generic-_625x300_08_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrink-driving-laws-in-india-all-you-need-to-know-5718325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20the%20minor%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20realtorwas%20reportedly%20seendrinking%20with%20friends%20at%20a%20Pune%20bar%2C%20the%2017-year-old%20crashed%20his%20Porsche%20car%20into%20a%20motorbike%2C%20killing%20two%20people%20on%20the%20spot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrink-driving-laws-in-india-all-you-need-to-know-5718325%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrink-driving-laws-in-india-all-you-need-to-know-571832