com%2Fauto%2Fcars%2Factor-naga-chaitanya-buys-rs-3-5-crore-porsche-gt3-rs-check-details%2Farticleshow%2F110323332.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drink%20Driving%20Charges%20Against%20Pune%20Teen%20Who%20Ran%20Over%20Techies%20With%20Porsche%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year-old%20who%20ran%20over%20two%20techies%20in%20Pune%20while%20driving%20a%20Porsche%20will%20be%20tried%20for%20drink%20driving%2C%20a%20juvenile%20court%20ruled%20today.%20The%20court%20said%20that%20he%20would%20be%20tried%20and%20punished%20under%20section%20185%20of%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20drink%20driving%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20states%20that%20drink%20driving%20is%20a%20criminal%20offense%20if%20a%20breath%20analyzer%20test%20reveals%20that%20the%20blood%20alcohol%20concentration%20of%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20motor%20vehicle%20is%20more%20than%2030%20mg%20per%20100%20ml.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20drink%20driving%20offence%20under%20the%20act%2C%20a%20person%20can%20get%20six%20months%20of%20jail%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20For%20a%20second%20offence%2C%20you%20could%20spend%20up%20to%202%20years%20in%20jail%20and%20be%20fined%20Rs%2015%2C000%20(up%20from%20Rs%203%2C000).%20Repeat%20offenders%20might%20also%20face%20penalties%20related%20to%20their%20driving%20licenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Sunday%2C%20two%20individuals%2C%20including%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20died%20after%20a%20Porsche%20collided%20with%20their%20motorcycle%20near%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20in%20Pune.%20The%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Anis%20Awadhiya%20and%20Ashwini%20Costa.%20The%20tragic%20incident%20occurred%20at%20about%203.15%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crash%20has%20sparked%20national%20outrage%20after%20the%20teenager%20was%20granted%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20on%20conditions%20that%20many%20have%20described%20as%20flimsy.%20A%20local%20court%20asked%20him%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20accidents%2C%20work%20with%20traffic%20police%20for%2015%20days%20and%20undergo%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECops%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20been%20drinking%20with%20his%20friends%20before%20the%20crash%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year-old%20who%20rammed%20his%20father's%20high-end%20Porsche%20knew%20that%20his%20act%20could%20cause%20death%20and%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20section%20against%20him%20will%20be%20applied%20accordingly%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Pune%20Police%20has%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%20the%20teenager%2C%20who%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20builder%2C%20was%20taken%20for%20a%20medical%20test%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20on%20Sunday%20and%20his%20blood%20has%20been%20taken%20and%20sent%20for%20a%20forensic%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716361860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2a0b8lo4_pune-teen-drinking-1200-_625x300_20_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrink-driving-charges-added-against-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-5718749%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2017-year-old%20who%20ran%20over%20two%20techies%20in%20Pune%20while%20driving%20a%20Porsche%20will%20be%20tried%20for%20drink%20driving%2C%20a%20juvenile%20court%20ruled%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrink-driving-charges-added-against-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-5718749%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrink-driving-charges-added-against-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-5718749%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrink-driving-charges-added-agai