stay%20on%20and%20work%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years%20after%20their%20degree%20course.%20But%20now%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20he%20will%20go%20for%C2%A0smaller%C2%A0changes%20to%20make%20the%20rules%20tighter%20and%20stop%20the%20immigration%20system%20from%20being%20misused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%C2%A0of%20the%20proposed%20ideas%C2%A0is%20to%20put%C2%A0tougher%C2%A0rules%20on%20agents%20advertising%20UK%20degree%20courses%20abroad.%20These%20agents%20may%20face%20penalties%20if%20they%20fail%20to%20deliver%20the%20quality%20of%20students%20they%20promise.%20Students%20from%20other%20countries%20who%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20UK%20with%20a%20graduate%20visa%20might%20have%20to%20take%20English%20tests.%20And%20if%20universities%20or%20colleges%20have%20too%20many%20students%20dropping%20out%2C%20they%20could%20lose%20their%20permission%20to%20recruit%20students%20from%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20announcement%20about%20these%20proposed%20changes%C2%A0is%20expected%C2%A0to%20come%20out%C2%A0at%20the%20same%20time%C2%A0as%20the%20Office%20for%20National%20Statistics%20releases%20its%20quarterly%20net%20migration%20figures%20on%20Thursday%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Guardian.%C2%A0It's%20predicted%C2%A0that%20these%20figures%20will%20still%20show%20high%20levels%20of%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20India%20sends%20a%20large%20number%20of%20students%20to%20study%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20more%20than%20almost%20any%20other%20country.%20They%20make%20up%20over%2040%25%20of%20all%20graduate%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fstudy-abroad-indian-students-body-in-uk-urges-pm-rishi-sunak-to-protect-graduate-route-visa-policy-5710292%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20students%20and%20alumni%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20asking%20Mr%20Sunak%20to%20keep%20the%20graduate%20visa%20programme.%20The%20National%20Indian%20Students%20and%20Alumni%20Union%20(NISAU)%20stressed%20that%20this%20visa%20route%20is%20crucial%20for%C2%A0keeping%C2%A0the%20UK%20attractive%20to%20international%20students.%20They%20disagreed%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20these%20visas%20only%20lead%20to%20low-paying%20gig%20economy%20jobs%2C%20saying%20they%20offer%C2%A0important%C2%A0chances%20for%20skilled%C2%A0jobs%C2%A0and%20career%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanam%20Arora%2C%20the%20chairperson%20of%20NISAU%2C%20told%20The%20Guardian%20that%20the%20best%20students%20would%20go%20to%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20best%20offer%20is%2C%20and%20any%20worsening%20of%20the%20graduate%20route%20will%20make%20the%20UK's%20offer%20significantly%20worse.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stated%20that%20international%20students%20are%20typically%20hard-working%20people%20who%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20into%20their%20education%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20alongside%20their%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20for%20a%20better%20future.%20%26quot%3BSome%20find%20merit%20in%20reducing%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20young%20people%20to%20%E2%80%98Deliveroo%20visas'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Arora%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20students%20take%20out%20costly%20educational%20loans%20to%20finance%20their%20studies.%20It's%20only%20fair%20that%20they%20expect%20some%20return%20on%20this%20substantial%20investment.%C2%A0What%20they%20seek%20is%C2%A0a%20straightforward%20opportunity%20to%20gain%20valuable%20work%20experience%20for%20a%20limited%20time%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%C2%A0Sunak's%20decision%C2%A0to%20step%20back%20about%20the%20more%20extreme%20plans%C2%A0comes%C2%A0after%20senior%20cabinet%20members%20like%20Chancellor%20Jeremy%20Hunt%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20David%20Cameron%2C%20Home%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20and%20Education%20Secretary%20Gillian%20Keegan%20opposed%20the%20idea.%C2%A0They%20said%20that%20strict%20limits%20on%20graduate%20visas%20would%20hurt%20both%20UK%20universities%20and%20the%20economy%C2%A0as%20a%20whole.%