ub%20came%20out%2C%20he%20signed%20up%2C%20like%20many%20restauranteurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20a%20necessary%20evil%2C%26quot%3B%20Marciante%2C%2055%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20he's%20weaning%20his%20restaurants%20off%20the%20apps.%20Marciante%2C%20who%20now%20has%20a%20second%20Chef%20Tony's%20location%20in%20Rockville%2C%20Maryland%2C%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20pizza%20concepts%2C%20said%20the%20tide%20appears%20to%20be%20turning%20and%20that%20other%20restaurant%20owners%20are%20also%20looking%20for%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20delivery%20apps%20have%20also%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20charging%20customers%20high%20fees%20and%20underpaying%20drivers.%20A%20recent%20study%20found%20customers%20who%20order%20takeout%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-postmates-food-delivery-costs-twice-as-much-as-pickup-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPostmates%20or%20DoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20paying%20twice%20as%20much%20for%20their%20meal.%20Meanwhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolden-age-gig-work-instacart-doordash-delivery-jobs-over-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelivery%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20BI's%20Alex%20Bitter%20that%20the%20job%20isn't%20as%20lucrative%20as%20it%20once%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20restaurateur's%20perspective%2C%20Marciante%20said%20there%20were%20two%20main%20drawbacks%20to%20using%20the%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20one%20issue%20was%20quality%20control%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20food-delivery%20apps%20don't%20always%20do%20enough%20to%20vet%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20customers%20dine%20in%2C%20the%20chef%20and%20restaurant%20staff%20can%20control%20the%20speed%2C%20presentation%2C%20and%20delivery%20of%20a%20meal%20from%20kitchen%20to%20table.%20But%20with%20the%20delivery%20apps%2C%20once%20the%20food%20goes%20in%20the%20takeout%20bags%20and