20to%20the%20usual%20food-delivery%20apps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20wean%20off%20the%20apps%2C%20Marciante%20now%20uses%20a%20white-label%20delivery%20service.%20Customers%20place%20their%20orders%20directly%20on%20the%20restaurant's%20website%2C%20and%20a%20third-party%20delivery%20service%20picks%20up%20and%20delivers%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarciante%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fowner-startup-for-independent-restaurants-fundraising-pitch-deck-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOwner.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20has%20raised%20millions%20in%20funding%20to%20help%20restaurants%20ditch%20the%20food-delivery%20apps.%20The%20company%20helped%20Marciante%20build%20out%20his%20website%20and%20his%20own%20app%20to%20take%20orders%20directly%20and%20has%20its%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F7-food-tech-delivery-startups-alternative-doordash-grubhub-ubereats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enetwork%20of%20delivery%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20pays%20about%20%24500%20per%20month%20per%20location%20for%20all%20the%20services%20and%20that%20Owner.com%20charges%20a%20flat%20delivery%20fee%20of%20%247%20per%20order%2C%20which%20can%20be%20paid%20by%20the%20restaurant%2C%20charged%20to%20the%20customer%2C%20or%20split%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarciante%20said%20he'd%20been%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-school-dropout-raises-millions-help-restaurants-curb-delivery-fees-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOwner.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20less%20than%20two%20months%20but%20was%20already%20super%20pleased%20with%20it%20and%20that%20he'd%20recommend%20it%20to%20other%20restauranteurs%20looking%20to%20get%20out%20from%20under%20the%20popular%20food-delivery%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20some%20of%20the%20apps%2C%20like%20Uber%20Eats%20and%20DoorDash%2C%20also%20offer%20white-label%20delivery%20services%2C%20where%20customers%20can%20place%20orders%20directly%20with%20a%20restaurant%20but%20they%20can%20be%20delivered%20by%20the%20app's%20drivers.%20This%20option%20will%20typically%20save%20the%20restaurant%20money%20compared%20to%20when%20customers%20order%20in%20the%20app%20itself%2C%20so%20it%20may%20be%20another%20option%20for%20restauranteurs%20to%20explore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarciante%20said%20DoorDash%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20after%20being%20contacted%20by%20BI%20and%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Boffered%20to%20up%20their%20game%26quot%3B%20working%20with%20him%20and%20assigned%20him%20a%20sales%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20food-delivery%20apps%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comments%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c502edb-9ef3-4d5e-9db2-202b20454184%5C%22%3EThe%20apps%20are%20useful%20for%20restaurants%20to%20get%20discovered%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20apps%20can%20be%20costly%20to%20restaurants%2C%20Marciante%20said%20they%20are%20still%20useful%20tools%20for%20restaurants%20to%20connect%20with%20first-time%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20will%20just%20pull%20up%20their%20phone%20and%20go%20to%20Uber%20and%20just%20figure%20out%20what%20they%20want%20to%20eat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20being%20in%20business%20for%2017%20years%2C%20Marciante%20has%20plenty%20of%20repeat%20customers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20order%20takeout%20or%20delivery%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%20Now%2C%20those%20customers%20can%20go%20straight%20to%20Chef%20Tony's%20website%20or%20app%20and%20place%20their%20orders%20rather%20than%20give%20a%20third-party%20app%20an%20increasingly%20high%20cut%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%20Marciante%20plans%20to%20maintain%20his%20presence%20on%20the%20apps%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20reaching%20new%20potential%20customers.%20But%20now%2C%20when%20those%20people%20find%20him%20and%20want%20to%20order%20from%20him%20again%2C%20they%20can%20go%20straight%20to%20his%20site%20and%20cut%20out%20the%20middleman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20restaurant%20owner%20who%20wants%20to%20share%20your%20experience%20using%20food-delivery%20apps%3F%20Have%20you%20stopped%20using%20the%20apps%20or%20are%20you%20trying%20to%20get%20off%20them%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akvlamis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ekvlamis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-owner-chef-moving-off-food-delivery-apps-doordash-ubereats-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716331888000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647dcf214fb5b23cc5e0c72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-owner-chef-moving-off-food-delivery-apps-doordash-ubereats-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maryland%20chef%20and%20restaurant%20owner%20Tony%20Marciante%20said%20food-delivery%20apps%20like%20DoorDash%20and%20Uber%20Eats%20were%20cutting%20too%20far%20into%20his%20margins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-owner-chef-moving-off-food-delivery-apps-doordash-ubereats-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Parthenope%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Paolo%20Sorrentino%20Crafts%20an%20Exquisite%20Treatise%20on%20Cinematic%20Beauty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716331560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FParthenope_fa81a9.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D