n%20breast%2C%20butter-chicken%20sauce%2C%20and%20basmati%20rice%20was%20just%20as%20delicious%20as%20takeout.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20loves%20Indian-inspired%20food%2C%20so%20I%20made%20a%20simple%20version%20of%20creamy%2C%20tangy%20butter%20chicken.%20For%20this%20meal%2C%20I%20used%20Burman's%20butter-chicken%20simmer%20sauce%20(%243.60)%2C%20a%20pack%20of%20Kirkwood%20chicken%20breasts%20(%245.60)%2C%20and%20Earthly%20Grains%2090-second%20microwavable%20basmati%20rice%20(%241.40).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20just%20over%20%2410%2C%20this%20nearly%20effortless%20meal%20was%20much%20cheaper%20than%20going%20out%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20air-fried%20veggies%20and%20sliced%20sausage%20for%20an%20easy%2C%20tasty%20meal%20that%20cost%20%2411.30.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pack%20of%20sausages%20with%20blu%20packaging%2C%20a%20bag%20of%20potatoes%2C%20broccoli%2C%20and%20a%20red%20and%20blue%20can%20of%20crescent%20rolls%20on%20a%20stone%20countertop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a64800dfb1341e9ff0762%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20kept%20things%20simple%20with%20sausage%2C%20crescent%20rolls%2C%20potatoes%2C%20and%20broccoli.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-easy-meals-to-make-in-air-fryer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair-fryer%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20sliced%20sausage%2C%20green%20vegetables%2C%20and%20potatoes.%20It's%20relatively%20healthy%2C%20hearty%2C%20and%20pairs%20well%20with%20buttery%20crescent%20rolls%2C%20which%20my%20kids%20like%20to%20snack%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20a%20package%20of%20Never%20Any!%20spinach-feta%20chicken%20sausage%20(%243.40)%2C%20broccoli%20(%242.60)%2C%20potatoes%20(%243.30)%