%20tablets.%20Other%20than%20its%20potential%20roles%20in%20human%20nutrition%2C%20donkey%20milk%20is%20used%20in%20ethnomedicine%2C%20and%20cosmetology%2C%20most%20likely%20due%20to%20its%20lysozyme%20content%2C%20and%20smoothing%20skin%20and%20scalp%20inflammations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20a%20potential%20business%20opportunity%2C%20Dhiren%20shifted%20his%20focus%20to%20set%20up%20a%20donkey%20farm%20in%20his%20village%20Manund%20of%20Patan%20district%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDidn%E2%80%99t%20get%20held%20up%20after%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20losses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Dhiren%20started%20TDS%20Donkey%20Farm%20without%20any%20formal%20training.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20also%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2037%20lakh%20to%20buy%2020%20donkeys%20and%20set%20up%20a%2040%C3%9730%20feet%20shed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20took%20the%20risk%20as%20I%20was%20confident%20and%20positive.%20But%20I%20overlooked%20the%20risk%20and%20my%20decision%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20purchase%20donkeys%2C%20milk%20them%20one%20day%2C%20and%20sell%20their%20milk%20the%20next%20day.%20This%20was%20not%20at%20all%20possible.%20I%20did%20not%20consider%20its%20low%20shelf%20life.%20There%20was%20no%20proper%20local%20market%20for%20it%20and%20it%20could%20not%20be%20sent%20abroad%20in%20its%20liquid%20form%20via%20plane%20or%20ship%20due%20to%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20year%2C%20he%20incurred%20losses%20up%20to%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20as%20he%20had%20to%20throw%203%2C000%20litres%20of%20milk%20down%20the%20drain.%20The%20only%20solution%20was%20to%20transport%20the%20milk%20abroad%20by%20converting%20it%20into%20dry%20powder%20form%20for%20transportation.%20But%20it%20took%20him%20a%20year%20to%20understand%20this%20and%20find%20suitable%20companies%20that%20did%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn