%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20not%20create%20their%20own%20brand%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20thought%20in%20mind%2C%20they%20approached%20a%20few%20of%20the%20smaller%20brands%20they%20worked%20with%20and%20asked%20them%20if%20they%20could%20sell%20their%20products%20under%20a%20private%20label.%20A%20few%20suppliers%20agreed%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20True%20Elements%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20True%20Elements%20scaled%20more%20than%20Healthy%20World%2C%20which%20made%20the%20founders%20pivot%20for%20the%20third%20and%20final%20time.%20They%20picked%20up%20the%20top-selling%20products%20from%20Healthy%20World%20and%20launched%20them%20through%20True%20Elements%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20another%20year%20before%20they%20could%20liquidate%20Healthy%20World%20and%20completely%20focus%20on%20building%20True%20Elements%2C%20which%20is%20a%20multi-crore%20brand%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20July%202017%2C%20True%20Elements%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94%20breakfast%20items%20like%20rolled%20oats%2C%20muesli%2C%20granola%2C%20and%20shakes%3B%20seeds%20like%20chia%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20flax%2C%20sunflower%2C%20watermelon%2C%20seed%20mixes%2C%20and%20trail%20mixes%3B%20peanut%20butter%2C%20dry%20fruits%2C%20berries%2C%20millets%2C%20millet%20flours%2C%20and%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20moved%20from%20a%20private%20label%20to%20manufacturing%20100%20percent%20of%20their%20own%20products%20in%202018%20from%20their%20sprawling%20factory%20in%20Pune%2C%20where%20over%20seven%20lakh%20of%20their%20products%20are%20manufactured%20each%20month.%20Their%20bestsellers%20are%20oats%2C%20chia%20seeds%20and%20muesli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Holding%20on%20to%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2013-year%20journey%20has%20been%20far%20from%20smooth.%20The%20duo%20pumped%